author: news@mpnews.net (Staff)
title: Youth soccer teams represent Mt. Pleasant well
text:
Youth soccer teams represent Mt. Pleasant well Oct 22, 2015 
Mt. Pleasant dominated the SESA Elite & Burlington Area YMCA Fall Leagues winning the U8, U12 and U14 divisions, all under the direction of Head Coach Ronald Carrillio, with support from Coaches Terry Jerrel, Dr. DeWayne Frazier and Sara Frazier. The U12 team pictured won the SESA Elite & Burling Area YMCA League, Conference and Cushman Cup officially on Saturday, Oct. 17, in Burlington at the Rec Plex. The U12 team is pictured from left to right: From Row: Spencer Hixon, Maverick Kerr, Tristian Shull, Moroni Sanchez and Jacob Richman. Back Row: Victor Sanchez, Isaac Jerrel, Gage Beauchamp, Sam Jerrel, Alexandra Carrillo and Nefi Sanchez. Not pictured: Blaine Frazier and Destiny Vargas, Head Coach Ronald Carrillo, Coach Terry Jerrel, Coach Dr. DeWyane Frazier and Coach Sara Frazier.
